data.title: "The Todo Latino Show" Interview with Pamela Rose Rodriguez (Podcast Episode 2021)
data.meta_description: Interview with Pamela Rose Rodriguez: Directed by Rafael Fernandez Jr., Brianna Fernandez. With Hannah Bouchard, Rafael Fernandez Jr., Brianna Fernandez, Maite Melian. Latin Babbler and the crew welcome special guest Pamela Rose Rodriguez. A Dominican/Cuban/American (Cubinican) singer/songwriter and actress. We showcase her music and talk about Latin holidays during quarantine as well as culture.
